{"tid":619750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四哥硬上！揭她童年起遭大哥性侵　媽知情卻罵女兒","createTime":"2018-04-07T03:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T06:04:32.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6af1ad82e12abb9eab72e169bab1951169bf48a8","tid":619750,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:20:24.000Z","msg":"1名少女3年前在KTV遭四哥性侵，查出她童年時多次遭大哥猥褻、性侵，媽媽的反應令她更心寒。<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，2015年9月30日少女被四哥帶往KTV與朋友一起歡唱，唱到最後友人離去，僅剩兄妹倆，四哥強行拖她進包廂廁所內性侵。法官依強制猥褻罪判他9月徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n檢方調查該案時，意外從少女臉書看到她從7、8歲起遭大哥多次性侵，媽媽也知情，甚至曾親眼看到衣衫不整的哥哥與她共處一室，少女說，「我媽知道的第一個反應就是打他，打完之後，卻是罵我」等語，也曾懷疑是否為媽媽親生。台中地院依加重強制猥褻罪將大哥判刑3年2月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180407/1329786\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180407%2F1329786&d=S3axBjbT7DzXQv2YFLyEHW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=00e30626\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180407%2F1329786&h=2506ca70\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180407/1329786</a><br />\n<br />\n好像Ｄ未亡人咁，俾成屋男親人屌曬"},{"pid":"5a22f88935af6730ee743b67371a67018b402150","tid":619750,"uid":5420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:21:21.000Z","msg":"以為謝老四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d839ca3b242ffc03d3a5aa42f4ad32ca6027676b","tid":619750,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:24:37.000Z","msg":"仲有大哥"},{"pid":"c55533ec0dbc3f86597723a2905f416b7279c967","tid":619750,"uid":64345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所</span></span>"},{"pid":"8d87037afd5a7195613f18f63328aea5988db82d","tid":619750,"uid":110969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T03:54:09.000Z","msg":"台中+1"}